data.description: This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits gracefully on an expansive corner lot, offering both space and comfort. Boasting a spacious kitchen adorned with white cabinets and granite countertops, it provides the ideal setting for family gatherings. The generous dining room invites family dinners and special occasions, while the ample family room offers a cozy retreat for relaxation and entertainment. Throughout most of the home, ceramic tile flooring enhances both aesthetics and practicality, offering durability and easy maintenance. Additionally, the property features a luxurious enclosed indoor swimming pool, promising year-round enjoyment and relaxation. For those with hobbies or projects, a large insulated workshop provides ample space for creativity and craftsmanship. Moreover, the property boasts a convenient 12x36 RV shelter/ boat, catering to outdoor enthusiasts and adventurers. House has a new roof and A/C in 2020. With its blend of comfort, functionality, and recreational amenities, this home offers a lifestyle of relaxation and enjoyment, making it an irresistible oasis for its fortunate inhabitants.
